AssetDisplayName: string; Asset display name (for example, 'My File Name.docx').
AssetExternalID: string; Unique identifier for an asset of this type. Format will vary by policy vendor.
AssetLink: string; URL to the asset. This may not be available for some policy vendors and asset types.
AssetMetadata: object; Metadata associated with the asset. Structure will vary by policy vendor.
DetectedTimestamp: int or string; Date and time the finding was first identified (for example, '2021-07-27T00:01:07Z').
FindingTypeDisplayName: string; Human-readable name of the finding type (for example, 'File Publicly Accessible Read Only').
FindingTypeID: string; UUID of the finding type in Cloudflare's system.
FindingTypeSeverity: string; Severity of the finding type (for example, 'High').
InstanceID: string; UUID of the finding in Cloudflare's system.
IntegrationDisplayName: string; Human-readable name of the integration (for example, 'My Google Workspace Integration').
IntegrationID: string; UUID of the integration in Cloudflare's system.
IntegrationPolicyVendor: string; Human-readable vendor name of the integration's policy (for example, 'Google Workspace Standard Policy').
